description: Enforce test coverage and code quality gates for TS and TSX changes
globs:
  - src/**/*.{ts,tsx}
  - "!src/**/*.spec.{ts,tsx}"
  - "!src/**/*.test.{ts,tsx}"
alwaysApply: true
---

# Quality gates

- Treat lint and formatting issues as blocking; do not finish with new lint or format errors.
- Keep imports clean by removing unused imports and organizing imports.
- For behavior changes in hooks, utils, or game logic, add or update tests in the same change.
- Prefer focused tests that cover behavior and edge cases.
- Do not weaken tests to pass CI; fix the root cause.
- If unrelated existing failures block progress, call them out clearly.

```ts
// Expected workflow for behavior change:
// 1) implement change
// 2) update or add tests
// 3) ensure lint and format pass
```
